<text top="1027" left="185" width="540" height="14" font="0">of a member of the delegation concerned to the Chief of the Verbatim Reporting Service, room </text>
<text top="1043" left="185" width="538" height="14" font="0">C-154A. Corrections will be issued after the end of the session in a consolidated corrigendum. </text>
<text top="1067" left="98" width="84" height="17" font="3">09-25276 (E) </text>
