<text top="334" left="90" width="70" height="17" font="5"><i>President</i>:<i> </i></text>
<text top="334" left="185" width="486" height="17" font="3">Mr.  D'Escoto  Brockmann  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . (Nicaragua) </text>
<text top="352" left="90" width="2" height="8" font="10"> </text>
<text top="361" left="90" width="2" height="8" font="10"> </text>
<text top="372" left="90" width="12" height="17" font="5"><i> </i></text>
<text top="372" left="126" width="336" height="17" font="5"><i>In the absence of the President, Mr. Wolfe </i></text>
<text top="390" left="126" width="276" height="17" font="5"><i>(Jamaica), Vice-President, took the Chair. </i></text>
<text top="407" left="90" width="2" height="8" font="10"> </text>
<text top="416" left="90" width="2" height="8" font="10"> </text>
<text top="426" left="90" width="290" height="17" font="5"><i>The meeting was called to order at 3.15 p.m. </i></text>
<text top="443" left="90" width="2" height="8" font="10"> </text>
